ked%20as%20a%20shipbroker%20for%20over%2015%20years%20and%20took%20comfort%20in%20his%20routine%20there.%20%26quot%3BEverything%20is%20at%20the%20back%20of%20my%20hand.%20I%20know%20everything.%20I%20know%20everyone.%20I%20have%20a%20regular%20salary%2C%20and%20I%20can%20go%20on%20holiday%20whenever%20I%20want%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20recalled.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20in%202022%2C%20his%20mother%2C%20Maryulis%20Bagindor%20Marlian%2C%20told%20him%20she%20was%20unwell.%20She%20was%2068%20then%20and%20had%20been%20running%20the%20business%20for%20almost%20three%20decades.%20Tambunan%20knew%20it%20was%20time%20to%20step%20in.%20%26quot%3BI%20took%20the%20plunge%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20told%20myself%20if%20I%20don't%20do%20it%20now%2C%20then%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20live%20to%20regret%20not%20knowing%20what%20I%20can%20do%20to%20the%20business.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22dad24d3b-d086-448d-946a-0852d8e132b0%5C%22%3EDealing%20with%20rising%20costs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224896%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Side%20dishes%20for%20nasi%20padang%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66ea544acfb7f307e5728df4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223264%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAt%20a%20nasi%20padang%20stall%2C%20diners%20can%20choose%20from%20a%20variety%20of%20sides%20to%20eat%20with%20their%20rice.%3Cp%3EErin%20Liam%2F%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETambunan%20said%20his%20mom%20was%20apprehensive%20at%20first.%20%26quot%3BShe%20knew%20that%20the%20good%20times%20of%20running%20a%20food%20and%20beverage%20business%20were%20going%2C%20going%2C%20gone%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERent%2C%20for%20one%2C%20had%20gone%20up.%20At%20one%20point%2C%20Tambunan%20said%20the%20rent%20for%20the%20store%20more%20than%20doubled%20after%20an%20investment%20firm%20took%20over%20the%20tenancy.%20He%20almost%20gave%20up%20and%20told%20his%20mom%20he%20planned%20to%