prices%20at%20Sabar%20Menanti.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20some%2010%20years%20ago%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-restaurants-where-to-eat-in-singapore%23old-airport-road-food-center-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplate%20of%20nasi%20padang%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20two%20sides%20would%20have%20cost%20less%20than%20SG%248.%20Now%2C%20he%20charges%20at%20least%20SG%2410%20for%20the%20dish.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstreet-food-in-singapore-2014-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENasi%20padang%3C%2Fa%3E%20involves%20a%20lot%20of%20labor%20and%20ingredients%20to%20cook%2C%20Tambunan%20explained.%20Beef%20rendang%2C%20a%20simmered%20beef%20dish%20cooked%20with%20coconut%20milk%20and%20spices%2C%20takes%20four%20to%20five%20hours%20to%20prepare.%20It's%20a%20three-person%20job%20to%20stir%2C%20cook%2C%20and%20watch%20the%20rendang%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmichelin-star-singapore-restaurant-hawker-stall-chef-nasi-lemak-food-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erise%20in%20prices%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20some%20customers%20have%20complained%2C%20Tambunan%20said.%20But%20others%20have%20understood%20the%20necessity%20of%20increasing%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAzreen%20Aziz%2C%2035%2C%20a%20regular%20who%20works%20nearby%2C%20is%20one%20of%20them.%20Preparing%20nasi%20padang%20is%20no%20simple%20task%2C%20she%20told%20me.%20%26quot%3BSome%20people%20will%20find%20it%20expensive%2C%20but%20we%20understand%20the%20work%20being%20put%20in.%26quot%3B%20Aziz%2C%20who%20usually%20visits%20with%20her%20colleagues%2C%20frequently%20chooses%20tauhu%20telor%2C%20an%20Indonesian%20tofu%20omelet%2C%20and%20sotong%20masak%20hitam%2C%20squid%20cooked%20in%20squid%20ink%20sauce%2C%20for%20her%20sides.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2224f5573c-8972-4157-989a-58fbb589c3f1%5C%22%3EKeeping%20up%20the%20quali