f%20an%20imminent%20ballistic%20missile%20attack%20against%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20exclusively%20to%20NDTV%2C%20Iran's%20Ambassador%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20Israel%20does%20not%20stop%20its%20hostility%20and%20its%20violations%20against%20the%20Iran's%20national%20interests%2C%20it%20will%20face%20such%20strikes%20again%20and%20again.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20went%20on%20to%20say%20that%20%26quot%3BPeople%2C%20not%20only%20in%20the%20region%2C%20but%20across%20the%20world%20are%20witnessing%20Israel's%20hostile%20moves%20in%20West%20Asia.%20Everyone%20is%20seeing%20the%20bloodshed%20in%20Gaza%20and%20south%20Lebanon.%20People%20are%20angry.%20Israel%20has%20violated%20all%20human%20rights%20treaties%2C%20all%20international%20laws%2C%20so%2C%20many%20people%20all%20over%20the%20world%20are%20very%20angry%20with%20what%20Israel%20is%20doing%20in%20the%20region.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ambassador%20further%20said%20that%20he%20believes%20Iran's%20missile%20attack%20on%20Israel%20will%20be%20%26quot%3Bsupported%20by%20many%2C%20many%20people%20around%20the%20world.%20You%20have%20seen%20how%20people%20marched%20in%20universities%20across%20the%20world%20protesting%20against%20Israel's%20brutality%20against%20Palestine.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ENETANYAHU'S%20WARNING%20AFTER%20IRAN%20MISSILE%20ATTACK%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Israeli%20PM%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20called%20Iran's%20missile%20attack%20on%20Israel%20%26quot%3BA%20failed%20attempt%26quot%3B%2C%20as%20Israel's%20Iron%20Dome%20and%20other%20mechanisms%20to%20stop%20such%20attacks%20prevented%20most%20of%20the%20180-plus%20missiles%20from%20hitting%20its%20territories%2C%20with%20only%20a%20few%20missiles%20penetrating%20its%20defence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Netanyahu%20also%20said%20that%20%26quot%3BIran%20made%20a%20big%20mistake%20tonight%20-%20and%20it%20will%20pay%20for%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20the%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20Mr%20Elahi%20referred%20to%20him%20as%20%26quot%3Bthe%20new%20Hitler%20of%20this%20century%26quot%3B.%20Repeating%20his%20statement%2C%20the%20Ambassador%20further%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20the%20Hitler%20of%20our%20time%20stops%20his%20brutality%20and%20hostility%2C%20then%20his%20country%20won't%20have%20to%20face%20the%20consequences%2C%26quot%3B%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3BIran%20will%20keep%20retaliating%20if%20Israel%20continues.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EAMERICA%20BACKING%20ISRAEL%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Joe%20Biden%20has%20come%20in%20support%20of%20Israel%20and%20condemned%20the%20%26quot%3Bprovocative%20escalation%26quot%3B%20by%20Israel%2C%20according%20to%20a%20statement%20by%20the%20White%20House.%20The%20US%20President%20ordered%20the%20US%20military%20to%20help%20Israel%20against%20any%20further%20missile%20attacks.%20The%20US%20reportedly%20also%20warned%20that%20areas%20from%20where%20missiles%20will%20be%20launched%20against%20Israel%20will%20be%20targeted%20by%20the%20US%20military.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommenting%20about%20US's%20support%20to%20Israel%2C%20the%20Ambassador%20told%20NDTV%20that%20%26quot%3BI%20hope%20the%20United%20States%20realises%20and%20reaches%20the%20conclusion%20that%20if%20they%20stop%20their%20support%20to%20Tel%20Aviv%2C%20Israel%20cannot%20carry%20on%20its%20crimes%20in%20the%20region.%20I%20hope%20the%20US%20Administration%20will%20convince%20Netanyahu%20and%20oblige%20(guide)%20him%20to%20stop%20the%20brutality.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20seen%20what%20America%20has%20done%20in%20Afghanistan%2C%20in%20Iraq%2C%20in%20Libya%2C%20and%20many%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20world.%20So%2C%20we%20believe%20that%20the%20US%20is%20behind%20many%20developments%20leading%20to%20the%20instability%20of%20the%20region%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20up%20to%20Israel%20now%20-%20whether%20they%20want%20to%20keep%20continuing%20this%20escalation%20or%20not%20(end%20it).%20If%20they%20continue%2C%20we%20will%20keep%20retaliating%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Elahi%20further%20said%2C%20suggesting%20that%20the%20ball%20is%20now%20in%20the%20court%20of%20%26quot%3Bthe%20decision%20makers%20of%20Israel%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EINDIA'S%20ROLE%20AS%20'FRIEND'%20OF%20BOTH%20IRAN%20AND%20ISRAEL%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Iranian%20Ambassador%20saiid%20he%20has%20always%20believed%20that%20%26quot%3BIndia%20is%20a%20very%20important%20player%20in%20the%20region.%20It%20has%20good%20relations%20with%20Israel%2C%20and%20as%20PM%20Modi%20has%20mentioned%20that%20this%20is%20not%20the%20era%20for%20war.%20We%20in%20Iran%20believe%20that.%20But%20if%20a%20country%20violates%20the%20sovereignty%20of%20another%20country%2C%20what%20else%20can%20that%20country%20do%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20hoped%20however%2C%20that%20%26quot%3BIndia%2C%20which%20has%20close%20ties%20with%20both%20sides%20(Iran%20and%20Israel)%2C%20can%20help%20convince%20Israel%20to%20stop%20its%20brutality%20in%20the%20region.%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727826840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fqqag0bd_benjamin-netanyahu-iran-supreme-leader-ayatollah-khamenei-reuters_625x300_02_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fndtv-exclusive-iran-ambassador-calls-israel-pm-benjamin-netanyahu-hitler-of-21st-century-says-india-can-help-stop-war-6696604%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Iran's%20Ambassador%20to%20India%20Iraj%20Elahi%20today%20said%20that%20his%20country%20will%20%26quot%3Bstrike%20Israel%20again%26quot%3B%2C%20if%20Tel%20Aviv%20doesn't%20refrain%20from%20attacking%20Tehran's%20national%20assets%20and%20interests%20in%20the%20region.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%2