%22%20title%3D%5C%22%E2%99%AC%20original%20sound%20-%20Gabe%20Escobar%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%E2%99%AC%20original%20sound%20-%20Gabe%20Escobar%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3C%2Fsection%3E%20%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20night%20before%20the%20shrimping%20trip%2C%20I%20slept%20below%20deck%20on%20the%20boat%20in%20a%20little%20bunk.%20And%20at%203%3A30%20a.m.%2C%20when%20it%20was%20still%20pitch%20black%2C%20we%20set%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20drove%20up%20the%20fjord%20for%20about%20two%20hours%20to%20the%20fishing%20spot%2C%20and%20then%2C%20by%206%20a.m.%2C%20we%20set%20sail%20on%20the%20trawler%20for%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBehind%20the%20boat%2C%20a%20big%20net%20scooped%20shrimp%20as%20we%20sailed.%20The%20crew%20dragged%20the%20net%20up%20when%20it%20was%20full.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20waiting%2C%20I%20spent%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20talking%20to%20the%20father-daughter%20duo%20who%20ran%20the%20business%2C%20and%20they%20told%20me%20about%20their%20jobs%20and%20their%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20net%20was%20pulled%20up%2C%20they%20put%20me%20to%20work.%20I%20helped%20sort%20the%20275%20pounds%20of%20shrimp%20and%20separate%20them%20from%20squids%2C%20little%20fish%2C%20and%20everything%20else%20that%20got%20pulled%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20shrimp%20are%20cooked%20on%20board.%20We%20then%20took%20a%20big%20bowl%20and%20sat%20on%20the%20front%20of%20the%20boat%2C%20where%20I%20was%20introduced%20to%20some%20traditional%20Norwegian%20summer%20food%20%E2%80%94%20toast%20with%20mayonnaise%2C%20shrimp%2C%20and%20lemon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20just%20me%20and%20the%20two%20of%20them%20on%20the%20little%20boat%2C%20so%20it%20felt%20really%20personal.%20This%20was%20a%20once-in-a-lifetime%20moment%2C%20and%20it%20has%20become%20one%20of%20my%20favorite%20adventures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225b388a5c-143f-47e8-974d-d25652fb7396%5C%22%3EOther%20side%20quests%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Escobar%20went%20backstage%20with%20the%20Norwegian%20band%20Stavangerkameratene%20while%20traveling%20in%20Oslo.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66ea78f9cfb7f307e5728efb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEscobar%20went%20backstage%20with%20the%20Norwegian%20band%20Stavangerkameratene%20while%20traveling%20in%20Oslo.%3Cp%3EGabe%20Escobar%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20wild%20one%20was%20when%20I%20went%20on%20tour%20with%20Stavangerkameratene%2C%20a%20Norwegian%20band%2C%20out%20to%20the%20middle%20of%20Norway.%20I%20spent%20a%20full%2024%20hours%20with%20the%20band%20and%20hung%20out%20with%20them%20backstage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20my%20side%20quests%20have%20turned%20out%20amazing%2C%20but%20there%20have%20been%20some%20times%20when%20even%20I%20have%20felt%20a%20little%20bit%20nervous.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%2C%20I%20was%20on%20a%20farm%2C%20and%20this%20woman%20and%20her%20husband%20approached%20me%2C%20asking%20if%20I%20wanted%20to%20see%20their%20horses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20that%20side%20quest%2C%20it%20occurred%20to%20me%20that%20getting%20into%20a%20car%20with%20two%20complete%20strangers%20might%20not%20be%20the%20best%20idea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227eda917c-0334-4d37-a1e2-3d202da5800c%5C%22%3ESome%20things%20they%20don't%20tell%20you%20about%20solo%20traveling%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Escobar%20on%20a%20hike%20in%20Europe.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66ea79efd17aa3c7b2b39e2c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEscobar%20on%20a%20hike%20in%20Europe.%3Cp%3EGabe%20Escobar%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20thing%20people%20don't%20tell%20you%20about%20solo%20traveling%20is%20how%20lonely%20it%20can%20be.%20The%20loneliness%20was%20exhausting%2C%20sometimes%2C%20because%20I'd%20try%20to%2