0firm%20was%20at%20%24650%20billion%2C%20it%20had%20grown%20between%2016%20or%2017%20times%20over%2C%20numbers%20that%20Rowan%20said%20are%20rare%20in%20financial%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20actually%20outgrew%20Apple%2C%20we%20outgrew%20Microsoft%2C%20%26quot%3B%20Rowan%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20outgrew%20almost%20every%20growth%20company%20you%20could%20think%20of.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20capital%20needs%20of%20the%20future%20are%20long-term%20and%20complex.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20slideshow%20that%20compares%20the%20needs%20of%20the%201890-1920s%2C%201990-2020%2C%20and%20then%20the%20needs%20of%202024%20and%20the%20future.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66fc5d075ccfc192a5525b33%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222250%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAccording%20to%20Apollo%2C%20we%20are%20entering%20a%20new%20financial%20era.%3Cp%3EApollo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EApollo%20forecasts%20up%20to%20%24100%20trillion%20in%20capital%20expenditures%20in%20three%20interconnected%20growth%20areas%20over%20the%20next%2010%20years%3A%20%2430%20trillion%20to%20%2450%20trillion%20in%20energy%20transition%2C%20%2430%20trillion%20in%20power%20and%20utilities%2C%20and%20%2415%20trillion%20to%20%2420%20trillion%20in%20digital%20infrastructure%20like%20data%20centers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20while%20banks%20and%20the%20capital%20markets%20fueled%20the%20last%20great%20era%20of%20growth%20amidst%20low%20interest%20rates%20and%20globalization%2C%20the%20firm%20thinks%20that%20this%20%26quot%3Bnew%20era%26quot%3B%20may%20look%20like%20a%20much%20older%20era%2C%201890%20to%201920.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20seen%20this%20movie%20before%2C%26quot%3B%20James%20Zelter%2C%20copresident%20of%20Apollo%20Asset%20Management%20said.%20Insurance%20companies%2C%20like%20New%20York%20Life%2C%20were%20the%20main%20sources%20of%20the%20capital%20necessary%20to%20finance%20the%20infrastructure%20of%20a%20new%20era%2C%20such%20as%20railroads%20and%20electrification.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20capital%20needs%20were%20long-dated%20at%20that%20point%20in%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Zelter%20said.%20With%20a%20new%20turn%20towards%20a%20new%20era%20of%20infrastructure%2C%20capital%20needs%20have%20again%20become%20much%20longer%20than%20the%20balance%20sheets%20of%20the%20banks%2C%20or%20the%20public%20capital%20markets%2C%20can%20handle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EApollo's%20ability%20to%20originate%20many%20different%20forms%20of%20capital%20is%20a%20differentiator.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22This%20slide%20compares%20Apollo%20Credit's%20lending%20capabilities%20with%20traditional%20lenders.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66fc5d6d5ccfc192a5525c11%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222250%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThis%20slide%20compares%20Apollo%20Credit's%20lending%20capabilities%20with%20traditional%20lenders.%3Cp%3EApollo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EApollo's%20merger%20with%20Athene%20brought%20life%20insurance%20and%20retirement%20capital%20to%20its%20balance%20sheet%20and%20is%20a%20key%20part%20of%20Apollo's%20future%20strategy.%20Athene's%20balance%20sheet%20has%20%24235%20billion%20in%20assets%20under%20management%2C%20plus%20an%20additional%20%2469%20billion%20from%20its%20Apollo-Athene%20dedicated%20investment%20program%2C%20and%20an%20additional%20%24392%20billion%20in%20third-party%20capital%20from%20clients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20capital%2C%20especially%20Athene's%20capital%2C%20which%20needs%20to%20pay%20out%20life-insurance%20annuities%2C%20is%20looking%20for%20long-term%2C%20safe%20yield.%20While%20many%20alternative%20firms%20are%20working%20with%20life-insurance%20capital%2C%20Apollo%20has%20brought%20it%20in-house.%20This%20allows%20the%20firm%20to%20lend%20in%20a%20wide-variety%20of%20ways%20over%20the%20long-term.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20banks%20scale%20back%20their%20own%20lending%2C%20Apollo%20expects%20to%20step%20in%20and%20finance%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20long-term%20solutions%20across%20a%20variety%20of%20cost%20of%20capital%20are%20not%20really%20appropriate%20for%20bank%20balance%20sheets%20who%20fund%20themselves%20short%2C%26quot%3B%20Rowan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAllocations%20towards%20fixed-income%20are%20up%2C%20providing%20a%20runway%20for%20the%20firm.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22This%20slide%20shows%20that%20allocations%20to%20fixed-income%20are%20back%20up%20to%2052%25%20this%20year%20after%20falling%20to%20as%20low%20as%204%25%20in%202022.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66fc5da49e0c5c2eeee9d0d6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222250%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThis%20slide%20shows%20that%20allocations%20to%20fixed-income%20are%20back%20up%20to%2052%25%20this%20year%20after%20falling%20to%20as%20low%20as%204%25%20in%202022.%3Cp%3EApollo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EApollo%20has%20its%20own%20capital%20to%20invest%2C%20but%20it%20also%20of%20course%20invests%20on%20behalf%20of%20other%20investors.%20And%20through%20that%20activity%2C%20it%20sees%20allocations%20to%20fixed-income%20and%20debt%2C%20rising%2C%20the%20firm's%20executives%20said%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20showed%20me%20the%20page%20from%201994%20to%202022%20and%20this%20is%20the%20allocation%20of%20fixed%20income%2C%20I%20would%20have%20told%20you%20it%20would%20be%20a%20horrific%20career%20decision%20to%20be%20in%20fixed%20income%20from%201994%20to%202022%2C%26quot%3B%20Zito%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20built%20our%20business%20as%20everybody%20was%20taking%20money%20out%20of%20fixed%20income.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20the%20firm%20grew%20multiple%20fixed-income%20business%20lines%2C%20which%20now%20should%20give%20it