%20targeted%20Hezbollah's%20military%20infrastructure%20across%20southern%20Lebanon%20and%20launched%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisrael-faces-dilemma-how-far-go-army-lebanon-hezbollah-experts-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eground%20offensive%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisrael-likely-used-bunker-buster-bombs-strike-kill-hezbollah-chief-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Israeli%20Air%20Force%20shared%20photos%20of%20F-15I%20fighter%20jets%3C%2Fa%3E%20loaded%20with%20what%20appeared%20to%20be%202%2C000-pound%20BLU-109%20bombs%20known%20as%20%26quot%3Bbunker%20busters%26quot%3B%20following%20the%20airstrikes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIran%20responded%20by%20launching%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Firan-attacks-israel-with-missiles-after-hezbollah-leader-killing-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emissile%20attack%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Israel%20on%20Tuesday.%20US%20warships%20helped%20intercept%20the%20Iranian%20missiles%2C%20and%20White%20House%20national%20security%20advisor%20Jake%20Sullivan%20said%20at%20a%20briefing%20Tuesday%20that%20Iran's%20attack%20was%20%26quot%3Bineffective.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisrael-airstrikes-lebanon-fighter-jets-raam-thunder-2024-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727818054000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66fc40077518aa57bc9fc9b9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisrael-airstrikes-lebanon-fighter-jets-raam-thunder-2024-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Israel%20Defense%20Force%20said%20it%20used%20fighter%20jets%20to%20target%20Hezbollah%20leaders%20in%20Lebanon.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tlakritz%40businessinsider.com%20(Talia%20Lakritz)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisrael-airstrikes-lebanon-fighter-jets-raam-thunder-2024-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Will%20Iran's%20Attack%20Lead%20To%20Full-Scale%20War%3F%20Israeli%20Spokesman%20Gives%20A%20Hint%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIsrael%20Defense%20Forces%20or%20IDF%20is%20currently%20assessing%20the%20missile%20attack%20by%20Iran%20today%20and%20an%20appropriate%20response%20will%20be%20given%20to%20Tehran%2C%20said%20Guy%20Nir%2C%20spokesperson%20of%20the%20Israeli%20embassy%20in%20India%2C%20speaking%20exclusively%20to%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIran%20today%20fired%20a%20barrage%20of%20missiles%20at%20Israel%20-%20nearly%20200%20of%20them%20-%20in%20its%20attempt%20to%20send%20a%20message%20to%20Tel%20Aviv%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20killings%20of%20the%20Hamas%20and%20Hezbollah%20chiefs.%20While%20Israel%20was%20able%20to%20block%20out%20most%20of%20the%20missiles%2C%20there%20were%20some%20that%20hit%20regions%20across%20the%20north%20and%20south%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20has%20been%20the%20sharpest%20escalation%20in%20tensions%20in%20West%20Asia%20(Middle%20East)%20since%20the%20start%20of%20the%20Israel%20Hamas%20war%20in%20Gaza%20nearly%20a%20year%20ago.%20Iran's%20Supreme%20leader%20Ayatollah%20Ali%20Khamenei%2C%20who%20is%20currently%20sheltered%20in%20a%20safe%20house%20at%20an%20undisclosed%20location%2C%20was%20the%20one%20who%20reportedly%20gave%20the%20green%20signal%20for%20the%20missile%20attack%20on%20Israel%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20NDTV%2C%20The%20Israel%20Embassy%20spokesperson%20warned%20that%20%26quot%3BIf%20he%20(Ayatollah%20Ali%20Khamenei)%20plans%20to%20initiate%20a%20full-scale%20war%20with%20Israel%2C%20it%20will%20be%20a%20mistake%20for%20them%20(Iran).%26quot%3B%20He%20went%20on%20to%20say%20that%20Israel's%20response%20to%20Tuesday's%20attack%20will%20be%20a%20strategic%2C%20pin-pointed%20one.%20%26quot%3BIsrael's%20response%20is%20going%20to%20be%20something%20strategic%20and%20pin-pointed%2C%20and%20not%20a%20full-scale%20war.%20I%20don't%20think%20any%20side%20wants%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20spokesperson%20also%20cautioned%20any%20other%20nation%20which%20might%20consider%20joining%20Iran%20to%20attack%20Israel.%20%26quot%3BIf%20any%20country%20is%20wanting%20to%20join%20Iran%2C%20all%20I%20can%20hope%20is%20that%20they%20don't%2C%20because%20if%20they%20do%2C%20the%20outcome%20will%20be%20devastating%20for%20them%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20warned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20Israel's%20top-notch%20defence%20mechanism%2C%20the%20Israeli%20spokesperson%20said%20that%20it%20is%20not%20just%20renowned%20'Iron%20Dome'%2C%20but%20other%20systems%20too%2C%20but%20did%20not%20give%20more%20details%20on%20what%20they%20are.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20not%20just%20the%20Iron%20Dome%2C%20we%20have%20many%20other%20defence%20systems%20in%20place%20that%20I%20cannot%20elaborate%20on%20for%20security%20reasons%2C%20which%20were%20helping%20us%20to%20bring%20this%20situation%20under%20control.%20The%20systems%20are%20very%20precise%20and%20out%20of%20over%20180%20missiles%2C%20most%20of%20them%20were%20not%20able%20to%20penetrate%20through%20these%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20spokesperson%20further%20confirmed%20that%20at%20the%20moment%20%26quot%3Bthere%20are%20no%20casualties%20in%20Israel%2C%20but%20there%20is%20one%20in%20Palestinian%20territories%26quot%3B.%20This%20he%20said%2C%20was%20because%20Iran%20targeted%20the%20entire%20region.%20He%20also%20explained%20how%20every%20Israeli%20national%20is%20prepared%20and%20trained%20for%20such%20scenarios%2C%20thereby%20preventing%20the%20loss%20of%20lives%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere%20is%20Israeli%20Embassy%20spokesperson%20Guy%20Nir's%20full%20interview%20to%20NDTV%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E