0Israeli%20citizens%20are%20out%20of%20their%20bunkers%20and%20shelters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EQ)%20What%20is%20the%20situation%20in%20Israel%20at%20the%20moment%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5CnA)%20Two%20hours%20ago%2C%20the%20Israel%20Defence%20Force%20of%20IDF%20had%20asked%20all%20citizens%20to%20go%20into%20shelters%20and%20bunkers%20to%20prepare%20for%20this%20attack.%20Around%20an%20hour%20ago%20we%20began%20to%20see%20missiles%20in%20the%20air%20and%20also%20falling%20all%20across%20Israel.%20All%20together%2C%20over%20180%20missiles%20were%20fired%20on%20Israel.%20As%20of%20now%2C%20the%20attack%20is%20finished%20and%20people%20are%20out%20of%20their%20shelters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EQ)%20Video%20footage%20shows%20that%20these%20missiles%20have%20hit%20many%20targets%20and%20there%20might%20by%20casualties.%20Do%20you%20have%20an%20update%20on%20this%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5CnA)%20So%20what%20we%20are%20seeing%20is%20that%20missiles%20have%20fallen%20across%20north%20and%20south%20Israel.%20These%20missiles%20have%20hit%20either%20buildings%20or%20in%20open%20areas.%20Up%20to%20now%2C%20we%20do%20not%20have%20any%20Israeli%20casualties%20as%20all%20Israelis%20went%20into%20their%20bunkers%20and%20safe%20rooms.%20However%2C%20there%20is%20one%20casualty%20in%20Palestinian%20territories%20as%20Iran%20launched%20missiles%20across%20the%20region.%20So%20currently%20we%20have%20confirmation%20of%20this%20one%20Palestinian%20person%20being%20killed%20in%20the%20Iran%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EQ)%20How%20efficient%20has%20the%20Iron%20Dome%20system%20been%20for%20Israel%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5CnA)%20It%20is%20not%20just%20the%20Iron%20Dome%2C%20we%20have%20many%20other%20defence%20systems%20that%20I%20cannot%20elaborate%20on%20for%20security%20reasons%2C%20which%20were%20helping%20us%20to%20bring%20this%20situation%20under%20control.%20The%20systems%20are%20very%20precise%20and%20out%20of%20over%20180%20missiles%2C%20most%20of%20them%20did%20not%20go%20through.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EQ)%20Do%20you%20think%20Israel%20will%20now%20attack%20Iran%20as%20well%20and%20this%20will%20turn%20into%20an%20all-out%20war%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5CnA)%20So%2C%20at%20the%20moment%20I%20want%20to%20be%20very%20cautious%20of%20what%20I%20am%20going%20to%20say.%20The%20IDF%20is%20currently%20assessing%20the%20situation%20to%20see%20what%20is%20going%20to%20be%20the%20proper%20way%20to%20respond.%20Will%20it%20be%20an%20all-out%20war%20or%20will%20it%20be%20something%20more%20strategic%3F%20Well%2C%20I%20guess%20Israel's%20response%20is%20going%20to%20be%20something%20more%20strategic%20and%20pin-pointed%20and%20not%20a%20full-scale%20war.%20I%20don't%20think%20any%20side%20wants%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EQ)%20As%20per%20reports%2C%20the%20Supreme%20leader%20of%20Iran%2C%20Ayatollah%20Khameni%2C%20is%20the%20one%20who%20had%20given%20the%20green%20signal%20for%20this%20missile%20attack.%20What%20is%20your%20take%20on%20this%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5CnA)%20I%20believe%20that%20if%20he%20plans%20to%20initiate%20a%20full-scale%20war%20with%20Israel%2C%20it%20will%20be%20a%20mistake%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EQ)%20It%20is%20believed%20that%20many%20other%20nations%20will%20join%20Iran%20in%20this%20war.%20Is%20Israel%20prepared%20for%20that%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5CnA)%20Israel%20is%20prepared%20for%20many%20scenarios.%20Israel%20is%20not%20alone.%20We%20have%20a%20number%20of%20our%20allies%20who%20will%20help%20us%20too.%20As%20for%20any%20country%20wanting%20to%20join%20Iran%2C%20all%20I%20can%20hope%20is%20that%20they%20don't%2C%20because%20if%20they%20do%2C%20the%20outcome%20will%20be%20devastating%20for%20them%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EQ)%20According%20to%20you%2C%20which%20countries%20might%20join%20Iran%20in%20this%20offensive%20against%20Israel%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5CnA)%20I%20hope%20none.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EQ)%20How%20is%20your%20family%20in%20Israel%3F%20Hope%20they%20are%20safe%20after%20this%20attack%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5CnA)%20I%20have%20spoken%20to%20my%20family%20after%20all%20this%20began.%20All%20of%20them%20are%20fine.%20I%20have%20a%20friend%20who%20lives%20very%20close%20to%20one%20of%20the%20areas%20that%20was%20attacked.%20I%20called%20her%20right%20away%20to%20make%20sure%20she%20was%20okay.%20All%20my%20family%20and%20relatives%20are%20fine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EQ)%20What%20is%20the%20kind%20of%20drill%20that%20most%20people%20in%20Israel%20are%20trained%20for%2C%20for%20such%20situations%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5CnA)%20So%2C%20every%20single%20person%20in%20Israel%20has%20a%20bunker%20or%20safe%20room%20in%20their%20homes%20-%20which%20have%20a%20double-sided%20wall%20which%20is%20unpenetrable%20for%20such%20missile%20attacks.%20All%20Israelis%20know%20and%20are%20trained%20that%20when%20there%20are%20alarms%2C%20they%20must%20get%20into%20their%20safe%20rooms%20within%20a%20specific%20time%20period%20given%20to%20them%20-%20which%20is%20usually%2060%20seconds%20to%20120%20seconds%2C%20depending%20on%20where%20you%20live.%20And%20we%20let%20them%20know%20in%20advance%20when%20they%20need%20to%20be%20close%20to%20a%20safe%20room%20as%20within%20the%20next%20hour%20or%20so%20there%20might%20be%20an%20alarm.%20The%20Israeli%20people%20always%20adhere%20to%20this.%20They%20are%20always%20prepared.%20They%20listen%20to%20these%20instructions%20very%20carefully.%20So%2C%20even%20today%2C%20when%20the%20final%20call%20happened%2C%20everyone%20was%20already%20close%20to%20a%20safe%20room%2C%20so%20they%20could%20go%20in%20fast%20and%20close%20the%20door.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EQ)%20So%2C%20every%20home%20or%20building%20across%20Israel%20has%20a%20safe%20home%20within%20it%20or%20attached%20to%20it%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5CnA)%20Yes%2C%20a%20majority%20of%20the%20homes%20in%20Israel%20have%20them.%20Since%201991%20we%20have%20a%20law%20which%2