2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20foreign%20ministry%20said%20at%2010.08%20pm%20IST%20that%20the%20missiles%20were%20fired%20a%20%26quot%3Bshort%20while%20ago%26quot%3B.%20An%20hour%20later%2C%20around%2011.10%20pm%2C%20the%20Israel%20Defence%20Forces%20(IDF)%20said%20there%20was%20no%20more%20threat%20from%20Iran%20%26quot%3Bfor%20now%26quot%3B%20and%20civilians%20could%20leave%20bomb%20shelters%2C%20adding%20that%20there%20were%20a%20few%20%26quot%3Bhits%26quot%3B%20during%20the%20barrage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConfirming%20the%20attack%2C%20Iran's%20Islamic%20Revolutionary%20Guard%20Corps%C2%A0said%20it%20was%20in%20response%20to%20the%20killing%20of%20Nasrallah%2C%20Hamas%20political%20chief%20Ismail%20Haniyeh%20and%20its%20own%20senior%20commander%20Abbas%20Nilforoushan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Revolutionary%20Guards%20also%20threatened%20to%20carry%20out%20%26quot%3Bcrushing%20attacks%26quot%3B%20against%20Israel%20if%20it%20retaliated%20after%20the%20attack.%20%26quot%3BIf%20the%20Zionist%20regime%20reacts%20to%20Iranian%20operations%2C%20it%20will%20face%20crushing%20attacks%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20carried%20by%20Iranian%20news%20agency%20Fars%2C%20according%20to%20news%20agency%20AFP.%C2%A0The%20Revolutionary%20Guards%20claimed%20the%20attacks%20were%20%26quot%3Bin%20accordance%20with%20the%20United%20Nations%20Charter%26quot%3B%20and%20came%20%26quot%3Bafter%20a%20period%20of%20restraint%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIran-backed%20Iraqi%20armed%20groups%20said%20US%20bases%20in%20Iraq%20and%20the%20region%20would%20be%20targeted%20if%20the%20United%20States%20joined%20any%20response%20to%20Iranian%20strikes%20on%20Israel%20or%20if%20Israel%20used%20Iraqi%20airspace%20against%20Tehran%2C%20news%20agency%20Reuters%20reported.%20Hamas%20praised%20the%20attacks%20as%20%26quot%3Bheroic%26quot%3B%20and%20celebrations%20were%20reported%20in%20Beirut.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Will%20Have%20Consequences'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20vowed%20to%20retaliate%20to%20the%20Iranian%20attack%2C%20with%20IDF%20Spokesperson%20Rear%20Admiral%20Daniel%20Hagari%C2%A0saying%20the%20country%20would%20respond%20at%20a%20time%20and%20place%20of%20its%20choosing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20attack%20will%20have%20consequences.%20We%20have%20plans%2C%20and%20we%20will%20operate%20at%20the%20place%20and%20time%20we%20decide%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20attack%20was%20taking%20place%2C%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20ordered%20the%20country's%20military%20to%20%26quot%3Baid%20Israel's%20defence%26quot%3B%20and%20shoot%20down%20Iranian%20missiles%20targeting%20its%20ally.%20A%20White%20House%20statement%20said%C2%A0%20Biden%20and%20Vice%20President%20Kamala%20Harris%2C%20who%20is%20the%20Democratic%20nominee%20in%20next%20month's%20US%20presidential%20election%2C%20were%20both%20monitoring%20Iran's%20attack%20on%20Israel%20from%20the%20White%20House%20situation%20room%2C%20AFP%20reported.%20The%20agency%20said%20some%20missiles%20had%20also%20been%20intercepted%20by%20neighbouring%20Jordan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVideos%20showed%20debris%20from%20missiles%20intercepted%20by%20Israel's%20famed%20Iron%20Dome%20and%20Arrow%20defence%20systems%20raining%20down%20on%20Tel%20Aviv.%20The%20Israeli%20Defence%20Forces%20also%20confirmed%20that%20blasts%20had%20been%20heard%20in%20%26quot%3BJerusalem%20and%20elsewhere%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ERAW%20FOOTAGE%3A%20Watch%20as%20Iranian%20missiles%20rain%20over%20the%20Old%20City%20in%20Jerusalem%2C%20a%20holy%20site%20for%20Muslims%2C%20Christians%20and%20Jews.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThis%20is%20the%20target%20of%20the%20Iranian%20regime%3A%20everyone.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FrIqUZWN3zy%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FrIqUZWN3zy%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Is