e.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Lokayukta%20and%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20have%20registered%20cases%20against%20Chief%20Minister%20Siddaramaiah%20in%20the%20alleged%20scam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMUDA%20Commissioner%20AN%20Raghunandan%20said%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20%26quot%3BAccording%20to%20the%20provisions%20of%20law%2C%20we%20can%20take%20back%20the%20plots%20of%20land.%20We%20discussed%20this%20with%20a%20panel%20of%20advocates.%20We%20took%20a%20decision%20to%20take%20the%20land%20back%20and%20we%20have%20instructed%20them%20to%20cancel%20the%20sale%20deed%20too.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20has%20no%20link%20with%20the%20investigation.%20We%20will%20inform%20the%20investigators%20if%20there%20is%20a%20probability%20to%20allot%20this%20to%20someone%20else.%20There%20are%20provisions%20in%20the%20law.%20We%20will%20inform%20the%20Lokayukta%20and%20other%20investigating%20officers%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20letter%20to%20the%20authority%2C%20Ms%20Parvathi%20said%20she%20wanted%20to%20return%20the%20plots%20earlier%20but%20was%20advised%20not%20to%20do%20so%20because%20the%20charges%20against%20her%20husband%20in%20the%20MUDA%20case%20were%20politically%20motivated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20husband%2C%20Siddaramaiah%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20of%20the%20state%2C%20has%20upheld%20a%20strict%20code%20of%20ethics%20throughout%20his%2040-year%20political%20career%2C%20remaining%20entirely%20free%20from%20any%20kind%20of%20blemish...%20To%20me%2C%20no%20house%2C%20plot%2C%20or%20wealth%20is%20more%20important%20than%20my%20husband's%20honour%2C%20dignity%2C%20and%20peace%20of%20mind.%20After%20all%20these%20years%20in%20power%2C%20I%20have%20never%20sought%20any%20personal%20gain%20for%20myself%20or%20my%20family%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20Siddaramaiah%20said%20his%20wife's%20decision%20to%20return%20the%20land%20-%20which%20he%20has%20maintained%20was%20gifted%20to%20her%20by%20her%20brother%20and%20encroached%20by%20MUDA%20-%20was%20her%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20have%20done%20no%20wrong%2C%20why%20should%20I%20resign%3F%20The%20land%20was%20de-notified%20by%20senior%20BJP%20leader%20and%20former%20Karnataka%20Chief%20Minister%20BS%20Yediyurappa%2C%20not%20by%20me.%20My%20legal%20team%20will%20fight%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20however%2C%20claimed%20the%20idea%20had%20come%20from%20the%20chief%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20this%20is%20a%20decision%20by%20Siddaramaiah's%20wife.%20It%20is%20a%20decision%20by%20him...%20this%20is%20like%20him%20admitting%20his%20mistake.%20But%20what%20has%20changed%20overnight%3F%26quot%3B%20asked%20BY%20Vijayendra%2C%20who%20is%20the%20Karnataka%20BJP%20chief%20and%20son%20of%20BS%20Yediyurappa.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727796180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Facnhg56_siddaramaiah-pti_625x300_17_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmysuru-urban-development-authority-muda-agrees-to-take-back-plots-from-siddaramaiahs-wife-6694122%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Mysuru%20Urban%20Development%20Authority%20(MUDA)%20has%20agreed%20to%20take%20back%2014%20plots%20of%20land%2C%20which%20have%20been%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20a%20massive%20row%20and%20an%20alleged%20scam%2C%20from%20the%20wife%20of%20Karnataka%20Chief%20Minister%20Siddaramaiah.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmysuru-urban-development-authority-muda-agrees-to-take-back-plots-from-siddaramaiahs-wife-6694122%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Biden%20was%20clear%20-%20so%20why%20is%20Israel%20defying%20its%20closest%20ally%20again%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727796060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3