d-single-digit%20decline%20in%20consolidated%20revenue%20for%20the%20quarter.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Flower-primary-sales-with-heavy-rain-in-q2-to-impact-profitability-dabur-124100101203_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Flower-primary-sales-with-heavy-rain-in-q2-to-impact-profitability-dabur-124100101203_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Flower-primary-sales-with-heavy-rain-in-q2-to-impact-profitability-dabur-124100101203_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Explained%3A%20How%20'The%20Quad'%20Faces%20A%20Big%20Challenge%20By%20China-Led%20Unnamed%20Bloc%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Quad%2C%20a%20strategic%20security%20grouping%20which%20was%20formed%20to%20maintain%20peace%2C%20stability%20and%20freedom%20of%20navigation%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20region%2C%20is%20facing%20a%20major%20challenge%20from%20an%20unofficial%2C%20unnamed%20alliance%20led%20by%20China%2C%20especially%20after%20the%20chronology%20of%20events%20in%20recent%20months%20leading%20up%20to%2C%20and%20beyond%20the%20latest%20Quad%20Summit%20in%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Quad%2C%20short%20for%20the%20Quadrilateral%2C%20is%20a%20group%20comprising%20India%2C%20the%20United%20States%2C%20Japan%2C%20and%20Australia.%20The%20grouping%20was%20formed%20with%20an%20aim%20to%20maintain%20security%20and%20freedom%20of%20navigation%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20and%20the%20Pacific%20Ocean.%20The%20Quad%20was%20first%20set%20up%20in%202007%2C%20but%20ceased%20to%20exist%20in%202008%20following%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20Australia.%20The%20group%20was%20re-established%20in%202017%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20then%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20then%20Japanese%20PM%20Shinzo%20Abe%2C%20and%20then%20Australian%20PM%20Malcolm%20Turnbull.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%2C%20which%20considers%20the%20grouping%20a%20threat%20to%20its%20expansionist%20policies%20in%20the%20South%20China%20Sea%2C%20Indian%20Ocean%20and%20Pacific%20Ocean%20regions%2C%20is%20now%20leading%20an%20unofficial%2C%20unnamed%20group%20to%20counter%20the%20Quad.%20The%20group%20comprises%20of%20China%2C%20Russia%2C%20Iran%20and%20North%20Korea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussia%2C%20which%20is%20facing%20an%20isolation%20from%20the%20West%2C%20especially%20United%20States%20and%20most%20of%20Europe%20over%20the%20Ukraine%20war%2C%20finds%20itself%20in%20a%20situation%20where%20it%20is%20heavily%20dependant%20on%20China%2C%20both%20economically%20as%20well%20as%20supply%20of%20select%20weaponry.%20Iran%20and%20North%20Korea%20too%2C%20find%20itself%20under%20heavy%20US%20sanctions%20and%20find%20itself%20in%20depending%20significantly%20on%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeijing%2C%20which%20aims%20to%20replace%20the%20United%20States%20as%20the%20leading%20global%20power%2C%20is%20leading%20its%20assertive%2C%20aggressive%20and%20expansionist%20policies%20by%20leveraging%20the%20ally's%20which%20are%20dependant%20on%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere%20are%20the%20chronology%20of%20provocative%20events%20led%20by%20China%20to%20send%20a%20message%20to%20the%20Quad%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EMESSAGE%20TO%20THE%20UNITED%20STATES%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20launched%20an%20intercontinental%20ballistic%20missile%20(ICBM)%20from%20its%20territory%20deep%20into%20the%20Pacific%20Ocean%20on%20September%2025%2C%20the%20first%20such%20test%20since%201980.%20The%20launch%20came%20days%20after%20the%20annual%20Quad%20Leaders'%20Summit%20was%20held%20in%20Delaware%20in%20the%20US.%20The%20ICBM%20can%20reportedly%20target%20any%20location%20in%20the%20US%20in%20less%20than%2030%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeijing%20has%20downplayed%20the%20incident%20calling%20the%20test%20-%20a%20first%20in%2044%20years%20-%20%26quot%3Broutine%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina's%20Ministry%20of%20National%20Defence%20or%20MND%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20People's%20Liberation%20Army%20Rocket%20Force%20(PLARF)%20launched%20an%20ICBM%20carrying%20a%20dummy%20warhead%20to%20the%20high%20seas%20in%20the%20Pacific%20Ocean%20at%2008%3A44%20on%20September%2025th%2C%20and%20the%20missile%20fell%20into%20expected%20sea%20areas.%20This%20test%20launch%20is%20a%20routine%20arrangement%20in%20our%20annual%20training%20plan.%20It%20is%20in%20line%20with%20international%20law%20and%20international%20practice%2C%20and%20is%20not%20directed%20against%20any%20country%20or%20target.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fja1odglo_china-icbm-reuters-_625x300_01_October_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20missile%20hit%20the%20desired%20target%20near%20the%20exclusive%20economic%20zone%20of%20French%20Polynesia%2C%20not%20far%20from%20the%20Marquesas%20Islands.%20China%20sent%20its%20Yuan%20Wang%205%20tracking%20ship%20near%20the%20landing%20site%20to%20collect%20data.%20New%20Zealand%20described%20the%20ICBM%20test%20as%20an%20%26quot%3Bunwelcome%20and%20concerning%20development%26quot%3B.%20The%20US%20Air%20Force%20too%20deployed%20an%20RC-135S%20Cobra%20Ball%20aircraft%20to%20collect%20optical%20and%20electronic%20data%20on%20the%20missile%20and%20its%20warhead%20about%20halfway%20along%20its%20flight%20path.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ICBM's%20desired%20target%20was%2012%2C000km%20from%20the%20launch%20site.%20The%20distance%20between%20China's%20Hainan%20Island%20and%20Los%20Angeles%20in%20the%20US%20is%20just%2012%2C100km.%20China%20therefore%20effectively%20demonstrated%20its%20ability%20to%20reach%20the%20US%20with%20this%20type%20of%20nuclear%20weapon%20in%20under%2030%20minutes.%20Beijing's%20newer%20DF-41%20has%20an%20even%20longer%20range.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20latest%20provocative%20test%20came%20at%20a%20time%20of%20heightened%20tensions%20with%20neighbours%20like%20Japan%2C%20the%20Philippines%20and%20Taiwan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaiwan's%20Ministry%20of%20Foreign%20Affairs%20immediately%20tweeted%2C%20%26quot%3BPLA's%201st%20ICBM%20launch%20in%2044%20years%20exposes%20the%20regime's%20expansionist%20ambitions%20%26amp%3B%20malign%20nature.%20Taiwan%20vehemently%20condemns%20the%20PRC%20for%20its%20reckless%20moves%20destabilising%20the%20region%20%26amp%3B%20urges%20China%20to%20exercise%20restraint%20%26amp%3B%20cease%20all%20actions%20that%20undermine%20global%20efforts%20for%20peace.%26quot%3B%20This%20was%20more%20than%20a%20routine%20test.%20China%20was%20sending%20a%20signal%2C%20an%20intimidating%20one%20at%20that%2C%20Teipei%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20has%20a%202009%20agreement%20with%20Russia%20for%20each%20side%20to%20notify%20the%20other%20of%20ballistic%20missile%20launches%2C%20but%20so%20far%20China%20has%20rejected%20all%20such%20suggestions%20for%20a%20similar%20mechanism%20with%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EMESSAGE%20TO%20JAPAN%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20September%2021%20-%20the%20day%20that%20the%20Quad%20Summit%20was%20held%20in%20the%20US%20-%20China%20began%20joint%20naval%20exercises%20in%20the%20Sea%20of%20Japan.%20Russia's%20Pacific%20Fleet%20had%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BA%20joint%20detachment%20of%20warships%20of%20the%20Pacific%20Fleet%20and%20Chinese%20Navy%20set%20out%20from%20Vladivostok%20to%20conduct%20the%20joint%20Russian-Chinese%20%26quot%3BBeibu%2FInteraction%20-%202024%26quot%3B%20naval%20exercise%2C%26quot%3B%20adding%20that%20the%20naval%20exercises%20will%20include%20anti-aircraft%20and%20anti-submarine%20weapons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20days%20into%20the%20joi