ref%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jiocinema.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Findia-vs-bangladesh-ashwin-interview-match-center-live%2F4029532%3FmediaID%3D4029532%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJio%20Cinema%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wasn't%20too%20pleased%20that%20I%20would%20be%20bowling%20again%20on%20the%20same%20day%2C%20and%20neither%20was%20Bumrah%20so%20that's%20the%20starting%20point.%20But%20obviously%20once%20you%20know%20you%20have%20to%20do%20it%2C%20you%20take%20your%20ice%20baths%2C%20hot%20baths%20and%20then%20start%20preparing%20for%20the%20bowling%20sessions.%20But%20look%2C%20I%20think%20what%20really%20sticks%20out%20for%20me%20is%20talking%20is%20one%2C%20but%20when%20you%20see%20the%20captain%20walking%20the%20talk%20%E2%80%93%20he's%20not%20played%20one%20ball%20with%20caution%20%E2%80%93%20he's%20just%20moved%20away%20and%20tonked%20the%20first%20ball%20for%20six.%20When%20Rohit%20does%20that%2C%20you%20don't%20have%20a%20choice%20but%20to%20follow%20it.%20So%20that%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20defining%20points%20of%20him.%20Talking%20about%20it%20is%20one%2C%20doing%20it%20another.%20And%20then%20talking%20and%20doing%20it%20altogether%20is%20a%20completely%20different%20kettle%20of%20fish%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20Ashwin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20India's%20successful%20series%20sweep%20over%20Bangladesh%2C%20Ashwin%20was%20crowned%20the%20Player%20of%20the%20Series%2C%20which%20was%20his%2011th%20title%20overall%20in%20Test%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20went%20level%20with%20Sri%20Lanka's%20legendary%20spinner%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Muttiah%20Muralitharan%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F313-muttiah-muralidaran-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMuttiah%20Muralitharan%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20also%20bagged%2011%20POTS%20awards%20during%20his%20illustrious%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Ashwin%20is%20not%20looking%20to%20compare%20himself%20with%20Muralitharan.%20For%20him%2C%20his%20exception