0live%20captioning%20and%20lyrics%20provided%20in%20song%20streaming%20platforms%20like%20Apple%20Music%20and%20Spotify.%20Apple%20Music%20also%20has%20a%20playlist%20curated%20by%20Deaf%20people.%20You%20can%20learn%20more%20about%20how%20Persons%20with%20Hearing%20Impairment%20experience%20music%20using%20this%20link.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20leads%20one%20to%20ask%20a%20deeper%20question%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20can%20having%20accessible%20cultural%20events%20come%20to%20be%20the%20norm%20rather%20than%20the%20exception%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20simple%20answer%20to%20that%20is%20by%20generating%20awareness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20participating%20in%20several%20festivals%20this%20year%20that%20will%20attract%20diverse%20audiences%2C%20and%20we%20hope%20to%20have%20sign%20language%20interpreters%20present.%20The%20number%20of%20people%20who%20understand%20sign%20language%20isn%E2%80%99t%20what%20matters%3B%20rather%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F334578%2Fcoda-child-of-deaf-adult-indian-sign-language-isl%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehaving%20sign%20language%20available%20helps%20raise%20awareness%20about%20its%20importance%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20simple%20presence%20can%20help%20everyone%20recognise%20and%20appreciate%20the%20Deaf%20community%2C%20which%20is%20a%20significant%20step%20toward%20greater%20understanding%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Jishnu%20when%20asked%20about%20what%20Swarathma%20plans%20for%20future%20concerts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20a%20glass-half-full%20perspective%2C%20sign%20language%20interpreters%20were%20rare%20in%20universities%2C%20workplaces%2C%20and%20courts%20just%20a%20decade%20ago.%20Today%2C%20however%2C%20they%20are%20increasingly%20becoming%20a%20common%20feature%20in%20these%20settings.%20With%20this%20positive%20shift%2C%20there%20is%20hope%20that%20such%20inclusivity%20will%20soon%20extend