24%2F09%2Fted1-1727447257-768x545.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fted1-1727447257-1200x852.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fted1-1727447257-150x106.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-367885%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221029%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWaste%20warriors%20at%20the%20Tieedi%20facility%20include%20a%20group%20of%20chickens%2C%20two%20rabbits%20expecting%20new%20friends%20soon%2C%20and%20two%20guinea%20pigs.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnimal%20integration%20is%20a%20major%20part%20of%20permaculture.%20The%20chickens%20eat%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20biodegradable%20material%2C%20and%20then%20they%20poop.%20That%20works%20as%20a%20catalyst%20in%20processing%20the%20biodegradable%20material%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20also%20have%20another%20important%20role%20%E2%80%94%20aeration.%20This%20is%20crucial%20for%20maintaining%20moisture%20and%20oxygen%20levels%20in%20the%20compost%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%20Aeration%20involves%20creating%20air%20pockets%20that%20allow%20enough%20oxygen%20to%20convert%20organic%20matter%20into%20compost.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20entire%20collection%20and%20composting%20process%20is%20done%20manually.%20The%20sloping%20terrain%20is%20utilised%2C%20allowing%20waste%20to%20be%20placed%20at%20a%20facility%20uphill%20from%20where%20it%20gently%20rolls%20down%20to%20the%20composting%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EReviving%20a%20stream%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99ve%20planted%20about%20600%20trees%20in%20the%20area%2C%E2%80%9D%20Utsow%20says%20when%20I%20ask%20him%20about%20the%20tiny%20river%20flowing%20through%20the%20compound.%20%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99ve%20also%20cut%20the%20hills%20into%20steps%20to%20allow%20water%20to%20recharge%20the%20soil%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20river%2C%20like%20several%20others%20flowing%20in%20the%20Shivaliks%2C%20is%20most%20active%20during%20the%20monsoon%20season.%20It%20is%20mostly%20rain-fed%20and%20often%20acts%20as%20a%20tributary%20to%20glacier-fed%20rivers%20like%20the%20Teesta%20and%20Ganga.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20particular%20stream%20has%20become%20perennial%2C%20Snehal%20informs%20me%2C%20explaining%20that%20the%20abundant%20groundwater%20provides%20a%20constant%20flow.%20Members%20of%20the%20Tieedi%20team%20have%20also%20placed%20nets%20along%20the%20stream%E2%80%99s%20borders%20to%20prevent%20people%20from%20dumping%20garbage.%20An%20interesting%20technique%20they%20employ%20is%20setting%20up%20a%20small%20temple%20at%20a%20part%20of%20the%20stream.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTreating%20it%20as%20an%20auspicious%20site%20prevents%20locals%20from%20dumping%20garbage%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20Snehal%20explains.%20A%20tiny%20bamboo%20bridge%20connects%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20complex%2C%20and%20the%20river%E2%80%99s%20constant%20flow%20adds%20melody%20to%20the%20voices%20of%20the%20many%20birds%20inhabiting%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201545px)%20100vw%2C%201545px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FDSCF8057_11zon_11zon-1727447382.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221545%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20bamboo%20bridge%20over%20the%20perennial%20stream%20leading%20to%20an%20eco-hut%20in%20Tieedi.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FDSCF8057_11zon_11zon-1727447382.jpeg%201545w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FDSCF8057_11zon_11zon-1727447382-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FDSCF8057_11zon_11zon-1727447382-500x375.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FDSCF8057_11zon_11zon-1727447382-768x576.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FDSCF8057_11zon_11zon-1727447382-1536x1152.jpeg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FDSCF8057_11zon_11zon-1727447382-1200x900.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FDSCF8057_11zon_11zon-1727447382-800x600.jpeg%20800w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FDSCF8057_11zon_11zon-1727447382-600x450.jpeg%20600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FDSCF8057_11zon_11zon-1727447382-400x300.jpeg%20400w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FDSCF8057_11zon_11zon-1727447382-200x150.jpeg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FDSCF8057_11zon_11zon-1727447382-150x113.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-367886%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221159%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EA%20bamboo%20bridge%20over%20the%20perennial%20stream%20leading%20to%20an%20eco-hut%20in%20Tieedi.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20numerous%20indigenous%20plants%2C%20including%20fruits%20and%20vegetables%2C%20are%20all%20grown%20organically.%20Mulching%20pits%2C%20neatly%20divided%20along%20the%20steps%2C%20assist%20in%20this%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Naya%20Basti%2C%20Badal%20tells%20me%20that%20Tieedi%E2%80%99s%20initiative%20has%20helped%20them%20better%20understand%20waste%20management%2C%20and%20they%20are%20now%20imparting%20this%20knowledge%20to%20the%20younger%20generations.%20He%20is%20also%20pleased%20that%20it%20is%20generating%20employment%20opportunities%20for%20the%20people.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20offer%20immersive%20experiences%20for%20travellers.%20We%20host%20events%20like%20Banbhaat%2C%20which%20is%20an%20art%2C%20music%2C%20and%20poetry%20festival%20steeped%20in%20local%20culture.%20We%20also%20organise%20the%20Darjeeling%20Eco-Trail%20run%2C%20which%20goes%20through%20the%20surrounding%20villages%2C%E2%80%9D%20Utsow%20informs%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHere%2C%20local%20delicacies%20like%20%3Cem%3Eselroti%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3Ealoodum%3C%2Fem%3E%20are%20featured%2C%20and%20the%20locals%20themselves%20are%20part%20of%20the%20whole%20programme%2C%20which%20helps%20us%20curate%20it%20in%20a%20very%20authentic%20way.%20We%20also%20promote%20bamboo%20weaving%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETieedi%E2%80%99s%20intervention%2C%20Utsow%20says%2C%20is%20also%20helping%20revive%20the%20bamboo%20industry%2C%20which%20people%20are%20gradually%20forgetting.%20Bamboo%20plays%20an%20important%20role%20in%20the%20buildings%20constructed%20within%20Tieedi%20as%20well.%20As%20I%20prepare%20to%20leave%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20greeted%20by%20Riwash%2C%20whose%20words%20I%20will%20carry%20home%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNature%20is%20important%3B%20it%20is%20absolute.%20We%20must%20learn%20to%20live%20in%20harmony%20with%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727450449000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FDSCF8112_11zon-1727442672.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D367839%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Utsow%20Pradhan%2C%20founder%20of%20Tieedi%2C%20left%20his%20corporate%20job%20to%20restore%20his%20ancestral%20land%20in%20Darjeeling%2C%20which%20had%20turned%20into%20a%20dumping%20ground.%20Through%20zero-waste%20initiatives%2C%20eco-trails%2C%20and%20community%20involvement%2C%20he%E2%80%99s%20creating%20sustainable%20villages%2C%20reviving%20local%20traditions%2C%20and%20helping%20restore%20the%20fragile%20Himalayan%20ecosystem.%20%E2%80%98Tieedi%2C%E2%80%99%20an%20acronym%20for%20%E2%80%9CTake%20It%20Easy%2C%20Easy%20Does%20It.%E2%80%9D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Arunava%20Banerjee%22%2C%22engagemen