-4-1726747608.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20restoration%20process%20took%20a%20total%20of%20two%20years%20before%20IF.BE%20was%20deemed%20ready%20to%20host%20events%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsustainable-architecture-4-1726747608.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsustainable-architecture-4-1726747608-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsustainable-architecture-4-1726747608-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsustainable-architecture-4-1726747608-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsustainable-architecture-4-1726747608-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-366757%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20restoration%20process%20took%20a%20total%20of%20two%20years%20before%20IF.BE%20was%20deemed%20ready%20to%20host%20events%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20have%20also%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F309116%2Fias-officer-anshul-gupta-efi-volunteers-restore-pond-wildlife-ujjain-madhya-pradesh%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efeatured%20in%20the%20restoration%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They%20are%20embedded%20in%20the%20glass%20floor%20towards%20the%20entrance.%20Another%20treasure%20lay%20in%20uncovering%20the%20historic%20gantry%20that%20once%20facilitated%20the%20transport%20of%20ice%20slabs.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20room%20was%20a%20%E2%80%98giant%20ice%20tray%E2%80%99%20where%20ice%20was%20manufactured.%20There%20were%20four-foot-deep%20pits%20with%20refrigerant%20coils%20running%20alongside%20that%20would%20freeze%20the%20water%20in%20the%20pits.%20The%20massive%20ice%20blocks%20were%20then%20picked%20up%20using%20a%