The%20team%20celebrates%20every%20employee%E2%80%99s%20achievements%2C%20fostering%20an%20environment%20free%20from%20jealousy.%20Each%20Friday%20concludes%20with%20%3Cem%3Echai%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20snacks%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Egupshup%3C%2Fem%3E%20(casual%20conversation)%2C%20providing%20a%20forum%20for%20employees%20to%20share%20any%20concerns%20or%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20implementing%20these%20and%20similar%20other%20practices%2C%20employers%20can%20create%20healthy%20workspaces%20where%20everyone%20feels%20valued.%20No%20one%20should%20feel%20overwhelmed%20or%20overworked%3B%20if%20you%20do%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20important%20to%20seek%20help.%20Ultimately%2C%20work%20is%20not%20everything.%20While%20your%20workplace%20may%20not%20remember%20you%2C%20your%20family%20and%20friends%20certainly%20will.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Anna%E2%80%99s%20mother%20poignantly%20stated%2C%20it%20is%20our%20collective%20responsibility%20to%20ensure%20that%20no%20other%20family%20or%20parent%20endures%20the%20pain%20they%20are%20experiencing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727186534000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FCopy-of-Infographic-website-2-1727184704.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D367326%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amidst%20viral%20conversations%20about%20toxic%20workplaces%20and%20their%20impact%20on%20employee%20well-being%20we%20highlight%20workplaces%20creating%20healthier%20environments.%20By%20integrating%20kindness%20into%20communication%2C%20offering%20flexible%20policies%2C%20and%20encouraging%20open%20dialogue%2C%20some%20organisations%20prioritise%20empathy%20and%20wellness%2C%20demonstrating%20how%20to%20build%20thriving%20workplaces%20where%20employees%20feel%20valued%20and%20supported.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindi