%20elusive%20creatures%20that%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20even%20have%20an%20accurate%20estimate%20of%20their%20population%20in%20the%20wild.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWell%2C%20in%20the%20hills%20of%20Manipur%2C%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20loss%20is%20finally%20evident.%20%E2%80%9CWithout%20pangolins%2C%20our%20crops%20are%20dying%2C%E2%80%9D%20exclaims%20Thomas%2C%20the%20Church%20catechist%20of%20Razai%20Khullen%20village.%20Pangolins%20and%20crops%20%E2%80%94%20what%20could%20be%20the%20connection%3F%20%E2%80%9COur%20houses%20are%20falling%20and%20our%20forests%20are%20decaying%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds%2C%20fuelling%20my%20curiosity%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20next%20week%2C%20I%20travel%20with%20a%20team%20of%20conservationists%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F360895%2Fvivek-menon-wildlife-trust-of-india-wildlife-conservation-anti-poaching-elephant-corridors%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWildlife%20Trust%20of%20India%20(WTI)%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20understand%20the%20implications%20and%20what%20is%20being%20done%20to%20ensure%20the%20survival%20of%20the%20pangolins%20in%20the%20hills%20of%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EJoining%20tribes%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20pangolins%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20am%20in%20Chingjaro%20%E2%80%94%20one%20of%20the%20last%20villages%20in%20the%20Indian%20state%20of%20Manipur%20%E2%80%94%20just%20a%20few%20kilometres%20from%20the%20borders%20of%20Myanmar.%20In%20between%2C%20are%20lush%20mountains%20connected%20by%20a%20narrow%2C%20remote%20and%20dodgy%20road.%20Long%20before%20reaching%20the%20border%2C%20you%20can%20already%20feel%20a%20distinct%20change%20in%20the%20surroundings.%20This%20place%20is%20nothing%20like%20Imphal%2C%20the%20state%20capital%20where%20I%20started%20my%20journey%20a%20few%20days%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManipur%20has%20been%20making%20headlines%20in%20recent%20years%20due%20to%20community%20clashes%20between%20the%20Meitei%2C%20Naga%20and%20Kuki%20tribes%20of%20the%20state.%20Hundreds%20of%20people%20have%20lost%20their%20lives%2C%20several%20homes%20have%20been%20burnt%20and%20thousands%20have%20been%20left%20homeless.%20The%20people%20have%20taken%20up%20arms%20to%20defend%20their%20territories%20and%20the%20tension%20is%20apparent%20everywhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20amidst%20the%20chaos%2C%20there%20is%20also%20a%20deep%20sense%20of%20unity%20and%20responsibility.%20While%20accompanying%20the%20team%20from%20the%20Wildlife%20Trust%20of%20India%2C%20I%20realised%20they%20have%20been%20working%20tirelessly%20amidst%20the%20turmoil%20to%20secure%20better%20protection%20for%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20most%20trafficked%20animal%20%E2%80%94%20the%20pangolin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202462px)%20100vw%2C%202462px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FFelicitating-community-leaders-of-Razai-Khullen-_-Manipur-_-Photograph-by-Madhumay-Mallik_11zon-1727101616.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222462%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Community%20leaders%20of%20Razai%20Khullen%20village%20are%20felicitated%20for%20their%20conservation%20efforts.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FFelicitating-community-leaders-of-Razai-Khullen-_-Manipur-_-Photograph-by-Madhumay-Mallik_11zon-1727101616.jpg%202462w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FFelicitating-community-leaders-of-Razai-Khullen-_-Manipur-_-Photograph-by-Madhumay-Mallik_11zon-1727101616-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FFelicitating-community-leaders-of-Razai-Khullen-_-Manipur-_-Photograph-by-Madhumay-Mallik_11zon-1727101616-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FFelicitating-community-leaders-of-Razai-Khullen-_-Manipur-_-Photograph-by-Madhumay-Mallik_11zon-1727101616-768x511.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FFelicitating-community-leaders-of-Razai-Khullen-_-Manipur-_-Photograph-by-Madhumay-Mallik_11zon-1727101616-1536x1022.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FFelicitating-community-leaders-of-Razai-Khullen-_-Manipur-_-Photograph-by-Madhumay-Mallik_11zon-1727101616-2048x1363.jpg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FFelicitating-community-leaders-of-Razai-Khullen-_-Manipur-_-Photograph-by-Madhumay-Mallik_11zon-1727101616-150x100.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-367230%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221638%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ECommunity%20leaders%20of%20Razai%20Khullen%20village%20are%20felicitated%20for%20their%20conservation%20efforts.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20we%20drive%20from%20Imphal%20to%20Ukhrul%2C%20Chingrisoror%20Rumthao%2C%20the%20field%20officer%20with%20WTI%E2%80%99s%20Countering%20Pangolin%20Trafficking%20Project%2C%20recounts%20his%20experiences.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20might%20seem%20completely%20out%20of%20place%20to%20talk%20about%20saving%20wildlife%2C%20when%20hundreds%20of%20people%20are%20getting%20murdered%2C%20but%20truth%20be%20told%2C%20there%20is%20still%20hope%2C%E2%80%9D%20exclaims%20Chingrisoror.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20also%20a%20community%20that%20has%20sustained%20on%20wild%20meat%20for%20generations.%20Over%20the%20past%20year%2C%20Chingrisoror%20has%20been%20travelling%20from%20village%20to%20village%2C%20talking%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20the%20pangolin%20and%20how%20the%20species%20is%20fast%20becoming%20rare%20in%20these%20hills.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20Tangkhul%20Naga%20himself%2C%20he%20understands%20the%20importance%20of%20hunting%20as%20part%20of%20both%20tradition%20and%20sustenance.%20%